title: How to have Project with submodules
body:
1. New parent Github repo
2. New Github repo for submodule
3. Add local git repo
4. Add remote parent github to local repo   
5. inside local git repo add new project with git repo
6. Add remote submodule github repo
7. Commit and push submodule repo
8. Commit and push parent git repo
